1. Create a mesh of a door which you want to add into the game.
2. A new object needs to be created, this will form your door hinge place this on the side of the door which you want to pivot.
3. Make the door hinge the parent of the door.
4. Add a box collider (this will make the tigger), make the the door the parent of the trigger.
5. The size of the trigger needs to be changed depending on how for you want the player distance to be before it opens.
6. Add the code to the trigger.
7. the angle of how the door opens is down to your prefrence this can be edited by the variables Angle X, Y and Z.
8. make the target your hinge object.
